This paper discusses the use of AI techniques for decision-making and preference elicitation, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of optimization techniques, which is a common topic in Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the use of qualitative preference statements, which is a topic in Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA) and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
